In the end, Orlando Cruz, upon seeing the number of people who expressed their
support upon his coming out, tweeted the following message:

>
> ‏[@ElFenomenoCruz](https://twitter.com/ElFenomenoCruz/status/254570595776339969):
> Buenos Dias Puerto Rico y New York y toda parte del Mundo Gracia por sus
> apoyos los quiero de todo Corazon su amigo Orlando Cruz.

>
> ‏[@ElFenomenoCruz](https://twitter.com/ElFenomenoCruz/status/254570595776339969):
> Good morning Puerto Rico, New York, and the rest of the world. Thank you for
> your support. I love you all from the bottom of my heart. Your friend,
> Orlando Cruz.

For more on the Orlando Cruz's story, read Hermes Ayala's excellent interview
for Noticel [here](http://www.noticel.com/noticia/131247/gancho-al-higado-de-
la-homofobia-soy-yo-soy-libre-video.html). [es]

